Type Description <code>Syntax</code> Syntax-highlighted code <code>SyntaxTheme</code> Color theme for highlighting <pre><code>use fast_rich::syntax::Syntax;
let syntax = Syntax::new(code, "rust");
</code></pre>

Type Description <code>Markdown</code> Markdown renderer <pre><code>use fast_rich::markdown::Markdown;
let md = Markdown::new("# Hello");
</code></pre>

Type Description <code>RichLogger</code> Log crate handler <code>ConsoleLog</code> Console-based logging <pre><code>use fast_rich::log::RichLogger;
RichLogger::init().unwrap();
</code></pre>

Type Description <code>Traceback</code> Pretty error display <code>TracebackConfig</code> Traceback options <code>install_panic_hook</code> Function to install panic handler <pre><code>use fast_rich::traceback::{Traceback, install_panic_hook};
install_panic_hook();
</code></pre>
